2011-09-09T07:40:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-09/wafer-works-corp-august-sales-fall-3-37-table-6182-tt.html
WAFER WORKS CORP (6182)  said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 3.37% to NT$441,831,000 from NT$457,228,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales            441,831          457,228    
YOY%              -3.37%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           4,067,446        3,013,129   
YOY%              34.99% 
=================================================================
 